text: Great batting cages indoors. I highly recommend them. You can choose baseball or softball. They have a very nice giftshop with all things baseball and softball. Prices are very reasonable for such a class act place. We've visited 4 times so far..

name: Alex Jihun Kim
text: I went with my son for the first time yesterday, but the system was not as difficult as I thought. The son who first started playing baseball understood easily. Women and young children can learn baseball without difficulty and are well equipped with safety helmets and nets. I think I will go there often with my son.

resp.text: Thank you for the 5 star review! We appreciate it! We hope to see you soon! We are so excited you and your son got the hang of the machines and enjoyed our facility! Thank you for supporting our small business

name: David Cybak
text: Great facility, and very well run!  I've been bringing both of my kids to D-BATS SW Birmingham since they opened, and they love it.  The place has everything your kid needs to get better-- huge cages that have tees, l-screens, and coaches stools; pitching mounds are set with multiple plates, so no need to move anything if one kid pitches from 60', and the other from 50.  Four of the cages have pitching machines, so one kid can workout in a cage while the other hits off the machines.  Plus, they offer lessons, have hit-trax technology.  Great place!

resp.text: Thank you for the review David!

resp.text: Thank you so much

name: Rick Dykes
text: Last night our 6U baseball team's practice was saved by the great staff at D-Bat. They held us two cages and we ran a pretty solid practice with 10 6 years olds for an hour. They had a slight scheduling mix up and had to give us one slightly smaller cage. To make up for it they gave us some some credits to hit balls from the pitching machine which was fun for the kids. All in all a great experience. Thanks again for making it work for us!

resp.text: Awesome! I’m so glad you all enjoyed it! Thank you for the 5 star review! We love our D-BAT family! We are glad we got to fit the team in for practices! Can’t wait to see y’all soon!!!
